(143, 31, '_edit_lock', '1417774593:1'),
(144, 32, 'section_one', 'Kempston-Parkes Chartered Surveyors may be a newly established company, but our business acumen and many years of experience of valuing and inspecting residential properties is solid and reputable.\r\n\r\nAndrew Kempston-Parkes, our Managing Director, is a well-respected, experienced member of The Royal Institution of Chartered Surveyors (RICS), having worked as a Chartered Surveyor in the residential property industry for over 14 years, within the Yorkshire region.\r\n\r\nBecause we are regional, we have an in-depth understanding of the local housing market and can confidently advise on the condition of all types of properties, and make accurate market valuations based on the breadth of our experience.'),
(145, 32, '_section_one', 'field_547efe2e3a4b1'),
(146, 32, 'section_two', 'We have extensive local knowledge of Harrogate, Knaresborough, Ilkley, Otley, Wetherby, Leeds, York, Ripon and surrounding areas and work with clients with properties of all sizes, ages and conditions.\r\n\r\nOver many years, Andrew has worked with a large number of clients to help move their house purchases forward efficiently and with ease. Or, when properties haven’t been quite up to scratch because of various defects identified through an inspection, his vigilance has helped clients to make an informed decision, even if this has meant not proceeding with the house purchase.'),
(147, 32, '_section_two', 'field_547efe763a4b2'),
(148, 32, 'section_three', 'Whatever the outcome, we strive for customer service excellence and our clients’ trust; always aspiring to maintain our reputation as the preferred Chartered Surveyors in your area. Repeat business is one of our measures of customer satisfaction, which is achieved through the high levels of personal service we offer. Andrew has personally worked with many clients, time and time again.'),
(149, 32, '_section_three', 'field_547efe833a4b3'),
(150, 2, 'section_one', 'Kempston-Parkes Chartered Surveyors is an established business with many years'' experience of valuing and inspecting residential properties.\r\n\r\nAll our surveyors are well-respected, experienced member of The Royal Institution of Chartered Surveyors (RICS), having worked as a Chartered Surveyor in the residential property industry for over 25 years, within the Yorkshire region.\r\n\r\nBecause we are local, we have an in-depth understanding of the housing market and can confidently advise on the condition of all types of properties, and make accurate market valuations based on the breadth of our experience.'),
(151, 2, '_section_one', 'field_547efe2e3a4b1'),
(152, 2, 'section_two', 'Our local knowledge extends across Yorkshire. We work with clients with properties of all sizes, ages and conditions.\r\n\r\nOver many years, we have worked with a large number of clients to help them make informed decisions about house purchases. Repeat business is one of our strengths and a true measure of customer satisfaction, which is achieved through high levels of customer service.'),
(153, 2, '_section_two', 'field_547efe763a4b2'),
(154, 2, 'section_three', 'We always strive for customer service excellence and our , clients’ trust; and aspire for a reputation as the preferred Chartered Surveyors in your area.'),
(389, 89, 'section_one', 'We understand that buying a property is a big emotional and financial commitment, so ensuring that your purchase is backed by the very best advice and guidance from an experienced and personable Chartered Surveyor, is vital to making an informed choice.\r\n\r\nWe will share your passion, excitement and anxieties; after all it’s part of taking that big step, whether it’s your first time on the property ladder or whether you have purchased property before.\r\n\r\nWhatever your requirements, we provide a full range of home surveys and inspections and residential property valuations. The service that is right for you depends on your particular property and individual requirements. Because we’re independent, we offer professional bespoke advice, tailored to your needs.\r\n\r\nKempston-Parkes, Chartered Surveyors already works with many established estate agents in your area, so you can instruct us to survey your property directly and independently.'),
(155, 2, '_section_three', 'field_547efe833a4b3'),
(156, 33, '_edit_last', '1'),
