(212, 43, 'text', '<blockquote>"Ensuring your house survey is credible and accurate is fundamental, and often the deciding factor, that makes or breaks a house purchase. So using the services of a reputable Chartered Surveyor is paramount.\r\n\r\nAt Kempston-Parkes Chartered Surveyors, we offer our clients a unique, more measured approach that is built on experience, integrity, personal service and strong client relationships."\r\n\r\n<footer>Andrew Kempston-Parkes<small>Managing Director</small></footer></blockquote>'),
