(80, 1, '2014-12-05 08:11:21', '2014-12-05 08:11:21', '<blockquote><p>"Ensuring 123 your house survey is credible and accurate is fundamental, and often the deciding factor, that makes or breaks a house purchase. So using the services of a reputable Chartered Surveyor is paramount.</p>\r\n<p>At Kempston-Parkes Chartered Surveyors, we offer our clients a unique, more measured approach that is built on experience, integrity, personal service and strong client relationships."</p>\r\n<footer>Andrew Kempston-Parkes<small>Managing Director</small></footer>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-05 08:11:21', '2014-12-05 08:11:21', '', 38, 'http://92.60.114.159/~kempstonparkesco/38-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
